---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---
<footer class="mt-24 border-t border-[color:var(--color-ink-line)]">
  <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-7xl gap-10 px-6 py-14 md:grid-cols-4 md:px-10">
    <div>
      <div class="font-[family-name:var(--font-display)] text-xl text-[color:var(--color-bone)]">Candle Atelier</div>
      <p class="mt-3 max-w-xs text-sm leading-relaxed text-[color:var(--color-bone-mute)]">
        A small London studio pouring coconut-rapeseed wax in hand-finished vessels.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <div class="text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-[color:var(--color-bone-mute)]">Shop</div>
      <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-sm">
        <li><a class="text-[color:var(--color-bone-dim)] hover:text-[color:var(--color-ember)]" href="/shop">All candles</a></li>
        <li><a class="text-[color:var(--color-bone-dim)] hover:text-[color:var(--color-ember)]" href="/cart">Your bag</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div>
      <div class="text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-[color:var(--color-bone-mute)]">Studio</div>
      <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-sm">
        <li><a class="text-[color:var(--color-bone-dim)] hover:text-[color:var(--color-ember)]" href="/about">The atelier</a></li>
        <li><a class="text-[color:var(--color-bone-dim)] hover:text-[color:var(--color-ember)]" href="/journal">Journal</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div>
      <div class="text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-[color:var(--color-bone-mute)]">Quiet letters</div>
      <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-[color:var(--color-bone-mute)]">
        Occasional notes. New pours. No noise.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="border-t border-[color:var(--color-ink-line)]">
    <div class="mx-auto flex max-w-7xl flex-col items-start justify-between gap-3 px-6 py-6 text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-[color:var(--color-bone-mute)] md:flex-row md:items-center md:px-10">
      <span>© {year} Candle Atelier</span>
      <span>Made quietly in the UK</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
